{"abstract":[{"text":"Inherited from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwitchComponentTokens.switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider\/switchsizewidthcursorunselected"]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeSwitchComponentTokensProviderC31switchSizeWidthCursorUnselectedSdvp","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena"}],"extendedModule":"OUDSThemesOrange","title":"switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"OUDSThemesOrange"}],"symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider\/switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of switch"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch \/ toggle"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSwitchComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"SwitchComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"switch \/ toggle","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Switch","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpacesSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") , sizes ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and opacities ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllOpacitiySemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeSwitchComponentTokensProvider/switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemeswitchcomponenttokensprovider\/switchsizewidthcursorunselected","title":"switchSizeWidthCursorUnselected","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThe